parameters:
Innkeeper: The most popular drink here is just water! When
it's too hot, people don't seem to want alcohol.

Innkeeper: Your throat must be dry. Please take your time
and rest.

Male Trainee: This sweltering heat... just wearing armor is
enough training.

Female Worker: It's so hot that I can't help but dress
lightly, hehe. It's not bad to have all the men's attention
to myself.

Male Worker: Do I look strange in this outfit? It's
comfortable for spending time in the desert.
